    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Machine learning is an interesting field of work and the full range of applications has yet to be researched. A commonly researched problem is that of stock prediction as it would potentially be one of the most profitable areas of research. Investors would be able to comfortably place their money in high performing companies and advancement would skyrocket as investment rose and companies detecting a decrease in productivity would be able to avoid crisis and get back on track. This problem is still very much open and much of the results so far are still in the range of comparable with random investment strategies and established stock brokerage firms.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
