*_f9gLvHDubWsM5q7 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/0*_f9gLvHDubWsM5q7 1400w"/><img alt="" loading="lazy" role="presentation" src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:700/0*_f9gLvHDubWsM5q7"></picture></div><br></div></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We can see here that our model is performing almost perfectly for quite a long time on completely unseen data. <strong>Our model is able to turn 1000.00USD into 1181.15USD with a sharpe ratio of 1.52 from the dates 2017–07–12 to 2018–02–08 (146 days) while just simply holding your money only increased your value to 1064.57.</strong> It cannot be understated how spectacular this result is, and what is even more impressive is that if I search for the best result on this range, the results are even better, whether by measure of maximal gains, lowest risks, or difference from the result of holding long term. The fact that the model diverges over time in places is mitigated by the fact that the model can be continually retrained every month or so with emerging data and new trends, even benefiting from the effects of transfer learning. Data can be gathered nightly and predictions can be ready before opening the next day.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
